data.title: MSSports: Registration
data.meta_description: Whether in football, horse riding, dancing, tennis, chess, biking, snow or poly sports, at MS Sports children and young people can expect a great experience with lots of new friends and unforgettable days dedicated to sport. In 2018, 10,501 children and young people took part in our Switzerland-wide camps and sweated, trained and had fun. When and where can we welcome your child? All information (dates, locations) can be found at www.mssports.ch/en<http://www.mssports.ch/en>. We look forward to seeing you!
data.text:
Registration

Search, find and select a camp. All camps are listed by date. Open the map to view all camps near you (click on the map section to open). You can also search with our Camp Finder. More information as well as prices can be found under "Camps" under the corresponding sport.

CAMPS DURING public HOLIDAYS?

Due to the numerous public holidays in Switzerland, some of which are regulated differently by the cantons, the MS Sports Camps also take place on public holidays (e.g. August 1, Assumption Day, etc.).
